cuss your HR requirements. We will be with you, communicate, guide and support you through the entirety of our working relationship.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer our HR services via the following packages:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Packages','','inherit','closed','closed','','25-revision-v1','','','2019-01-29 09:00:01','2019-01-29 09:00:01','',25,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/25-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(27,1,'2019-01-29 09:00:11','2019-01-29 09:00:11','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>What do we offer?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>SERVICES</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nWhiteTree HR offer a range of services to compliment your business. Whether you want to ensure you are legally compliant, streamline your processes, develop your strategic HR, or need advice and assistance with your every day operational HR, White Tree HR is here for you. We will work with you to allow your business to thrive and develop.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','23-revision-v1','','','2019-01-29 09:00:11','2019-01-29 09:00:11','',23,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/23-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(28,1,'2019-01-29 09:02:07','2019-01-29 09:02:07','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Let us tell you more.<br></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>EXPERIENCE COUNTS</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>White Tree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux in 2016. Stephanie has 12 years experience as a HR Generalist working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups &amp; SMEâs to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to SMEâs and local businesses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During her time in HR, Stephanie ha