pyright/Company Info','copyright_company_info','publish','closed','closed','','field_5c517f2fdd73d','','','2019-01-30 10:41:14','2019-01-30 10:41:14','',83,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/?post_type=acf-field&p=88',2,'acf-field','',0),(89,1,'2019-01-30 12:22:23','2019-01-30 12:22:23','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Let us tell you more.<br></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>EXPERIENCE COUNTS</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>White Tree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux in 2016. Stephanie has 12 years experience as a HR Generalist working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups &amp; SMEâs to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to SMEâs and local businesses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within businesses at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides business Managers and the board with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','28-revision-v1','','','2019-01-30 12:22:23','2019-01-30 12:22:23','',28,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/28-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(90,1,'2019-01-30 12:22:58','2019-01-30 12:22:58','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Let us tell you more.<br></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>EXPERIENCE COUNTS</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>White Tree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux in 2016. Stephanie has 12 years experience as a HR Generalist working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups &amp; SMEâs to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to SMEâs and local businesses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within businesses at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides business Managers and the board with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','28-revision-v1','','','2019-01-30 12:22:58','2019-01-30 12:22:58','',28,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/28-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
