mes_flickr\";s:0:\"\";s:32:\"startpoint_threecolumn_fet_desc1\";s:214:\"Assisting businesses with the day to day management of their HR. Including, Employment Law, Absence Management, Policies and Procedures, Employee Relations, Recruitment and Resourcing, Performance and Appraisals. \n\";s:32:\"startpoint_threecolumn_fet_desc2\";s:342:\"We work with your business, the management team and key stakeholders to deliver innovative, bespoke and diligent strategic HR services that include Talent Management, Reward Management, Employee Engagement and Retention, Organisational Structure, Management Development, Acquisitions and Mergers including TUPE, Restructures and Redundancy. \n\";s:32:\"startpoint_threecolumn_fet_desc3\";s:252:\"Collaborating with businesses on HR projects, working with you from the initial concept to completion and implementation. WhiteTree HR can also review, analyse and improve existing projects or aid development of ongoing projects within your business. \n\";s:32:\"startpoint_threecolumn_fet_desc4\";s:239:\"WhiteTreeHR are specialists in HR Software and the management of employee data, as well as Employee Self portals. We are able to help with all of your Management Information, Key Performance Indicators, Data Analysis and reporting needs. \n\";s:32:\"startpoint_threecolumn_fet_desc5\";s:259:\"We are HR Administration experts here at WhiteTree HR. We work with you and your business to alleviate this time consuming, yet integral part of HR so that your time is freed to focus on business essentials without having the worry of everyday necessities.  \n\";s:32:\"startpoint_threecolumn_fet_desc6\";s:125:\"Take our free WhiteTree HR Health Check questionnaire to help you understand how healthy your current HR practices are today!\";s:15:\"startpoint_logo\";s:0:\"\";}','yes'),(197,'startpoint_option_migrate','1','yes'),(418,'category_children','a:0:{}','yes'),(454,'new_admin_email','stephanie@whitetreehr.co.uk','yes'),(463,'recently_activated','a:0:{}',