ing packages </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Administration </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Policies and procedures </li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data entry </li><li>Document management </li><li>Recruitment administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:18:28','2019-03-07 11:18:28','',5,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2019-03-07 11:18:57','2019-03-07 11:18:57','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR offer a range of services to compliment your business. Whether you want to ensure you are legally compliant, streamline your processes, develop your strategic HR, or need advice and assistance with your every day operational HR, White Tree HR is here for you. We will work with you to allow your business to thrive and develop. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Operational HR</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employee\nHandbook </li><li>Policies\nand Procedures </li><li>Terms\nand Conditions and employee contracts </li><li>Absence\nManagement </li><li>Disciplinary\nand Grievance </li><li>Recruitment\nand Resourcing </li><li>Reward\nManagement </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Strategic HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Talent\nmanagement </li><li>Mergers\nand Acquisitions (Inc. TUPE) </li><li>Management\nTraining </li><li>Organisational\nStructure </li><li>Redundancy\n(reword?) </li><li>Employee\nengagement </li><li>Management\nDevelopment </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Project HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A comprehensive service to aid you\nin any HR project. We provide a bespoke and diligent service to be allow you to\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Data Analysis and HR Systems</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employee\nInformation Management and Storage </li><li>Key\nPerformance Indicators (KPIâs) </li><li>Management\nInformation (MI) </li><li>Data\nAnalysis and Reporting </li><li>Weekly,\nMonthyl, Quarterly, annual reporting packages </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Administration </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Policies and procedures </li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data entry </li><li>Document management </li><li>Recruitment administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:18:57','2019-03-07 11:18:57','',5,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2019-03-07 11:20:13','2019-03-07 11:20:13','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR offer a range of services to compliment your business. Whether you want to ensure you are legally compliant, streamline your processes, develop your strategic HR, or need advice and assistance with your every day operational HR, White Tree HR is here for you. We will work with you to allow your business to thrive and develop. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Operational HR</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employee\nHandbook </li><li>Policies\nand Procedures </li><li>Terms\nand Conditions and employee contracts </li><li>Absence\nManagement </li><li>Disciplinary\nand Grievance </li><li>Recruitment\nand Resourcing </li><li>Reward\nManagement </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Strategic HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Talent Management </li><li>Mergers and Acquisitions (Inc. TUPE) </li><li>Management Training </li><li>Organisational Structure </li><li>Redundancy (reword?) </li><li>Employee Engagement </li><li>Management Development </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Project HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A comprehensive service to aid you\nin any HR project. We provide a bespoke and diligent service to be allow you to\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Data Analysis and HR Systems</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employee Information Management and Storage </li><li>Key Performance Indicators (KPIâs) </li><li>Management Information (MI) </li><li>Data Analysis and Reporting </li><li>Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Annual reporting packages </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Administration </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Policies and Procedures </li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data Entry </li><li>Document Management </li><li>Recruitment Administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:20:13','2019-03-07 11:20:13','',5,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,'2019-03-07 11:22:35','2019-03-07 11:22:35','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR are an innovative, dynamic and diligent HR Consultancy. We pride ourselves on being flexible, bespoke and reliable enabling us to deliver premium HR solutions that work for you and your business.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux. Stephanie is CIPD qualified and has 12 years experience working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups, SMEâs to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to small local businesses. During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within organisations at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides Business Managers, Key Stakeholders and Executives with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2019-03-14 13:30:31','2019-03-14 13:30:31','',0,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/?page_id=10',-3,'page','',0),(11,1,'2019-03-07 11:22:35','2019-03-07 11:22:35','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux in 2016. Stephanie has 12 years experience as a HR Generalist working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups, SMEâs to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to small local businesses. During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within organisations at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides Business Managers, Key Stakeholders and Executives with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:22:35','2019-03-07 11:22:35','',10,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(12,1,'2019-03-07 11:27:11','2019-03-07 11:27:11','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please complete the contact form below and we will get back to you (Name, email&lt; Contact Number, Brief description of service required, Preffered method of contact </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Alternatively  you can email or call us at:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Email: enquires@whitetreehr.co.uk</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Phone: xxxxxx</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:27:11','2019-03-07 11:27:11','',2,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(13,1,'2019-03-07 11:29:12','2019-03-07 11:29:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here at WhiteTree HR we pride ourselves on being diligent and innovative whilst creating bespoke solutions. We are perfectly positioned to collaborate with businesses on HR projects within their organisations, working with you from concept to completion. Whatever your requirements we are here to support your business. We can provide advice, guidance, reports, reviews or complete projects for you. Contact us today to discuss how we can help you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Create bespoke HR projects</li><li>Aid businesses in completion of\nprojects </li><li>Review existing projects, analyse\nand improve existing projects or compliment the development of ongoing projects\nwithin the business</li><li>Project integration </li><li>Project documentation </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Project HR','','trash','closed','closed','','project-hr__trashed','','','2019-03-14 10:58:13','2019-03-14 10:58:13','',0,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),(14,1,'2019-03-07 11:29:12','2019-03-07 11:29:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here at WhiteTree HR we pride ourselves on being diligent and innovative whilst creating bespoke solutions. We are perfectly positioned to collaborate with businesses on HR projects within their organisations, working with you from concept to completion. Whatever your requirements we are here to support your business. We can provide advice, guidance, reports, reviews or complete projects for you. Contact us today to discuss how we can help you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Create bespoke HR projects</li><li>Aid businesses in completion of\nprojects </li><li>Review existing projects, analyse\nand improve existing projects or compliment the development of ongoing projects\nwithin the business</li><li>Project integration </li><li>Project documentation </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Project HR','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:29:12','2019-03-07 11:29:12','',13,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(17,1,'2019-03-07 11:33:40','2019-03-07 11:33:40','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR offer a range of services to compliment your business. Whether you want to ensure you are legally compliant, streamline your processes, develop your strategic HR, or need advice and assistance with your every day operational HR, White Tree HR is here for you. We will work with you to allow your business to thrive and develop. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Operational HR</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employee\nHandbook </li><li>Policies\nand Procedures </li><li>Terms\nand Conditions and employee contracts </li><li>Absence\nManagement </li><li>Disciplinary\nand Grievance </li><li>Recruitment\nand Resourcing </li><li>Reward\nManagement </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Strategic HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Talent Management </li><li>Mergers and Acquisitions (Inc. TUPE) </li><li>Management Training </li><li>Organisational Structure </li><li>Redundancy (reword?) </li><li>Employee Engagement </li><li>Management Development </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Project HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A comprehensive service to aid you\nin any HR project. We provide a bespoke and diligent service to be allow you to\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Data Analysis and HR Systems</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employee Information Management and Storage </li><li>Key Performance Indicators (KPIâs) </li><li>Management Information (MI) </li><li>Data Analysis and Reporting </li><li>Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Annual reporting packages </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Administration </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Policies and Procedures </li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data Entry </li><li>Document Management </li><li>Recruitment Administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HR Healthcheck</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Our free HR Healthcheck provides an initial guide to where you are with your HR requirements </li><li>Further to this we can ensure that you are up to date with current employment legislation and are legally compliant with a review of your current policies and procedures with a clear and detailed report of recommendations </li><li>Action plans provided </li><li>Policies, procedures, terms and conditions along with employee handbooks are available from WhiteTreeHR </li><li>Annual updates as and when changes come into place via the government along with any changes in employment legislations to ensure that you stay compliant </li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree\'s HR Health check provides you with an independent, objective, impartial review of your policies and procedures. This enables you to highlight and mitigate any risk, reduce cost, improve and drive performance through your people, ultimately adding value to your organisation. Taking into account the complexities of employment legislation as well as government updates, we will review and assess your current policies and procedures and report back to you clearly highlighting any areas of improvement, potential exposure, legal compliance and actions you can take. Our approach is always bespoke to fit the needs of your dynamic business and we tailor our solutions packages allowing you to pick and mix to meet your exact requirements.Â  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Take our free health check questionnaire to help you understand how\nhealthy your HR is today!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:33:40','2019-03-07 11:33:40','',5,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(18,1,'2019-03-07 11:47:57','2019-03-07 11:47:57','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Coming soon!! Watch this space.... </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','News and Blog','','publish','closed','closed','','news-and-blog','','','2019-03-14 13:22:59','2019-03-14 13:22:59','',0,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/?page_id=18',0,'page','',0),(19,1,'2019-03-07 11:47:57','2019-03-07 11:47:57','','News and Blog','','inherit','closed','closed','','18-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:47:57','2019-03-07 11:47:57','',18,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/18-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(20,1,'2019-03-07 11:54:58','2019-03-07 11:54:58','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606266\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606266\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR offer a selection of packages to suit our clients needs. We aim to be bespoke, affordable, innovative and conscientious of our clients business needs and requirements. We have detailed our most popular packages but are completely flexible in our approach, as experience tells us, no single business is the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Bamboo Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âpay as you goâ package for ultimate flexibility, whether it be by the hour or day. Discounts are offered for multiple and regular requirements. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Oak Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âretentionâ package for stability and a guaranteed set service. Perfect for businesses that require a fixed number of hours, days or onsite visits per week/month/year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Juniper Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âOnsiteâ visits package. Great if you need or prefer a face to face HR presence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Aspen Package</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âProject HRâ package. Ideal for your business if you have a specific HR project that you would like to create, transform, implement or integrate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Elder Tree Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Systems, Data and Management Information (HRMI)â package. Suitable for any business that requires requires regular or ad hoc data analysis, statistics and reports. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Maple Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Auditâ Package. For businesses that would like their current HR processes and documentation reviewing with advice provided on current legal compliance and any suggested amendments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Birch Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âEssential HRâ package provides you with the HR foundations for your business, including Terms and Conditions and Employee Handbook. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><a href=\"http://whitetree.localhost/contact\">Contact us</a> for your Free Consultation today!  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our packages serve as a guide. We are a bespoke HR Consultancy and will work with you to provide the right HR support for you and your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Packages','','publish','closed','closed','','packages','','','2019-03-25 14:28:33','2019-03-25 14:28:33','',0,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/?page_id=20',-1,'page','',0),(21,1,'2019-03-07 11:54:58','2019-03-07 11:54:58','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Packages</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR offer a selection of packages to suit our clients needs. We aim to be bespoke, affordable, innovative and conscientious of our clients business needs and requirements. We have detailed our most popular packages but are completely flexible in our approach as experience tells us, no single business is the same. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact us today for a free consultation to\ndiscuss how we can help you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hourly </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer an hourly rate, usually purchased in\nblocks of 4. Discounts for multiple and regular&nbsp;\nblocks purchased </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Daily </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using the same principal as our hourly rate. We offer discount for multiple and regular days and we have options for onsite visits as well as remote. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pay as you go â hourly and daily </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our Hourly and Daily rates are available on a\npay as you go basis, specifically with our Small â Medium business client in mind.\nThis enables them to be more flexible and have the same HR Support without\ncommitting to a set plan or cost.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Project</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We can offer fixed price quotes for bespoke\nprojects. Please get on contact with us today to see how we can help. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HR Management Information Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you require MI information every month,\nevery quarter, annually or even a one off report, then we have packages to suit\nyour needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Annual HR Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You receive a set number of remote HR support hours,\nhowever many suits your business requirements, along with legal updates\nthroughout the year to ensure that you are working with the most up to date and\nrecent employment legislation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HR Audit Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WhiteTree HR will review your current HR\npolicies and procedures and provide you with a detailed, clear report of\nsuggested improvements. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Essential HR Package </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This package contains your HR essentials. You and\nprocedures your company requires as well as a template offer letter and terms\nand conditions. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pick and Mix </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please contact us for a free consultation if\nyou are interested in more than one of the packages above. We are a bespoke HR\nConsultancy and will work with you to provide you with the right HR support for\nyour business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Packages','','inherit','closed','closed','','20-revision-v1','','','2019-03-07 11:54:58','2019-03-07 11:54:58','',20,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/07/20-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(22,1,'2019-03-07 14:22:09','