!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Administration </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Policies and Procedures </li><li>Employee Handbook</li><li>Letters </li><li>Data Entry </li><li>Document Management </li><li>Recruitment Administration </li><li>Ad hoc HR Administration </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>HR Healthcheck</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Our free HR Healthcheck provides an initial guide to where you are with your HR requirements </li><li>Further to this we can ensure that you are up to date with current employment legislation and are legally compliant with a review of your current policies and procedures with a clear and detailed report of recommendations </li><li>Action plans provided </li><li>Policies, procedures, terms and conditions along with employee handbooks are available from WhiteTreeHR </li><li>Annual updates as and when changes come into place via the government along with any changes in employment legislations to ensure that you stay compliant </li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree\'s HR Health check provides you with an independent, objective, impartial review of your policies and procedures. This enables you to highlight and mitigate any risk, reduce cost, improve and drive performance through your people, ultimately adding value to your organisation. Taking into account the complexities of employment legislation as well as government updates, we will review and assess your current policies and procedures and report back to you clearly highlighting any areas of improvement, potential exposure, legal compliance and actions you can take. Our approach is always bespoke to fit the needs of your dynamic business and we tailor our solutions packages allowing you to pick and mix to meet your exact requirements.&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Take our free health check questionnaire to help you understand how\nhealthy your HR is today!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2019-03-13 14:50:02','2019-03-13 14:50:02','',5,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/13/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(73,1,'2019-03-13 14:50:58','2019-03-13 14:50:58','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR offer a range of services to compliment your business. Whether you want to ensure you are legally compliant, streamline your processes, develop your strategic HR, or need advice and assistance with your every day operational HR, WhiteTree HR is here for you. We will work with you to allow your business to thrive. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Operational HR</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Assisting your businesses with the day to day management HR. Operational HR areas that we cover include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Employment Law </li><li>Employee Relations</li><li>Absence Management </li><li>Recruitment and Resourcing  </li><li>Performance and Appraisals </li><li>Policies and Procedures </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Strategic HR </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We work with your business, the management team and key stakeholders to deliver innovative, bespoke 