!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Following on from WhiteTree\'s HR Health Check, our HR Audit provides you with an independent, objective, impartial review of your policies and procedures. This enables you to highlight and mitigate any risk, reduce cost, improve and drive performance through your people, ultimately adding value to your organisation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Further to this we can provide employment legislation, government updates and we will review and assess your current policies and procedures and report back to you clearly highlighting any areas of improvement, potential exposure, legal compliance and actions you can take. Our approach is always bespoke to fit the needs of your dynamic business and we tailor our solutions packages allowing you to pick and mix to meet your exact requirements.&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Our free HR Health Check provides an initial guide to where you are with your HR requirements </li><li>Further to this we can ensure that you are up to date with current employment legislation and are legally compliant with a review of your current policies and procedures with a clear and detailed report of recommendations </li><li>Action plans provided </li><li>Policies, procedures, terms and conditions along with employee handbooks are available from WhiteTreeHR </li><li>Annual updates as and when legal changes come into place along with any changes in employment legislations to ensure that you stay compliant </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Take our free HR Health Check questionnaire to help you understand how healthy your HR is today!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 12:48:36','2019-03-14 12:48:36','',5,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/14/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(99,1,'2019-03-14 12:50:29','2019-03-14 12:50:29','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606266\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606266\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR offer a selection of packages to suit our clients needs. We aim to be bespoke, affordable, innovative and conscientious of our clients business needs and requirements. We have detailed our most popular packages but are completely flexible in our approach, as experience tells us, no single business is the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Bamboo Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âpay as you goâ package for ultimate flexibility, whether it be by the hour or day. Discounts are offered for multiple and regular requirements. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Oak Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âretentionâ package for stability and a guaranteed set service. Perfect for businesses that require a fixed number of hours, days or onsite visits per week/month/year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Juniper Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âOnsiteâ visits package. Great if you need or prefer a face to face HR presence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Aspen Package</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âProject HRâ package. Ideal for your business if you have a specific HR project that you would like to create, transform, implement or integrate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Elder Tree Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Systems, Data and Management Information (HRMI)â package. Suitable for any business that requires requires regular or ad hoc data analysis, statistics and reports. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Maple Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Auditâ Package. For businesses that would like their current HR processes and documentation reviewing with advice provided on current legal compliance and any suggested amendments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Birch Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âEssential HRâ package provides you with the HR foundations for your business, including Terms and Conditions and Employee Handbook. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><a href=\"http://whitetree.localhost/contact\">Contact us</a> for your Free Consultation today!  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our packages serve as a guide. We are a bespoke HR Consultancy and will work with you to provide the right HR support for you and your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Packages','','inherit','closed','closed','','20-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 12:50:29','2019-03-14 12:50:29','',20,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/14/20-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(100,1,'2019-03-14 13:22:59','2019-03-14 13:22:59','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Coming soon!! Watch this space.... </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','News and Blog','','inherit','closed','closed','','18-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 13:22:59','2019-03-14 13:22:59','',18,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/14/18-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(101,1,'2019-03-14 13:26:24','2019-03-14 13:26:24','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Hello world!','','inherit','closed','closed','','1-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 13:26:24','2019-03-14 13:26:24','',1,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/14/1-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(102,1,'2019-03-14 13:30:31','2019-03-14 13:30:31','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR are an innovative, dynamic and diligent HR Consultancy. We pride ourselves on being flexible, bespoke and reliable enabling us to deliver premium HR solutions that work for you and your business.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR was founded by Stephanie DeVeaux. Stephanie is CIPD qualified and has 12 years experience working for a wide variety of companies from Start Ups, SMEâs to large national, international and global companies. She has worked within a number of industries from Manufacturing to Legal, Government to small local businesses. During her time in HR, Stephanie has headed up a number of HR projects, worked closely with a variety of HR Systems and integrated extensively within organisations at both an Operational and Strategic level. She provides Business Managers, Key Stakeholders and Executives with a comprehensive and professional HR service along with ensuring companies work within current employment legislation and to best practice standards. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 13:30:31','2019-03-14 13:30:31','',10,'http://beta.whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/14/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(103,1,'2019-03-14 22:13:53','2019-03-14 22:13:53','{\n    \"startpoint_options[startpoint_slideimage1]\": {\n        \"value\": \"http://whitetreehr.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/header-whitetree-improved.png\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-03-14 22:13:53\"\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','ce18b550-8959-4041-8150-0c0f36a70f08','','','2019-03-14 22:13:53','2019-03-14 22:13:53','',0,'http://whitetreehr.co.uk/2019/03/14/ce18b550-8959-4041-8150-0c0f36a70f08/',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(104,1,'2019-03-14 22:35:24','2019-03-14 22:35:24','{\n    \"startpoint_options[inkthemes_linked]\": {\n        \"value\": \"https://linkedin.com/company/whitetreehr\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-03-14 22:34:59\"\n    },\n    \"startpoint_options[inkthemes_instagram]\": {\n        \"value\": \"https://instagram.com/whitetree_hr\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-03-14 22:34:59\"\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','3e17da29-2773-4463-97e1-319fc9b168e2','','','2019-03-14 22:35:24','2019-03-14 22:35:24','',0,'http://whitetree.localhost/?p=104',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(105,1,'2019-03-14 22:38:23','2019-03-14 22:38:23','{\n    \"startpoint_options[inkthemes_instagram]\": {\n        \"value\": \"https://instagram.com/whitetree_hr/\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-03-14 22:38:23\"\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','91336bab-76ba-4ea7-9603-f7bb30743d49','','','2019-03-14 22:38:23','2019-03-14 22:38:23','',0,'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/14/91336bab-76ba-4ea7-9603-f7bb30743d49/',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(106,1,'2019-03-14 22:40:10','2019-03-14 22:40:10','{\n    \"startpoint_options[inkthemes_twitter]\": {\n        \"value\": \"https://twitter.com/whitetreehr1\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-03-14 22:40:10\"\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','fe257647-99d7-4a26-8913-b89cbb5dcfda','','','2019-03-14 22:40:10','2019-03-14 22:40:10','',0,'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/14/fe257647-99d7-4a26-8913-b89cbb5dcfda/',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(107,1,'2019-03-25 14:25:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2019-03-25 14:25:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://whitetree.localhost/?p=107',0,'post','',0),(109,1,'2019-03-25 14:28:23','2019-03-25 14:28:23','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606266\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606266\" class=\"has-text-color\">WhiteTree HR offer a selection of packages to suit our clients needs. We aim to be bespoke, affordable, innovative and conscientious of our clients business needs and requirements. We have detailed our most popular packages but are completely flexible in our approach, as experience tells us, no single business is the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Bamboo Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âpay as you goâ package for ultimate flexibility, whether it be by the hour or day. Discounts are offered for multiple and regular requirements. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Oak Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âretentionâ package for stability and a guaranteed set service. Perfect for businesses that require a fixed number of hours, days or onsite visits per week/month/year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Juniper Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âOnsiteâ visits package. Great if you need or prefer a face to face HR presence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Aspen Package</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âProject HRâ package. Ideal for your business if you have a specific HR project that you would like to create, transform, implement or integrate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Elder Tree Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Systems, Data and Management Information (HRMI)â package. Suitable for any business that requires requires regular or ad hoc data analysis, statistics and reports. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Maple Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âHR Auditâ Package. For businesses that would like their current HR processes and documentation reviewing with advice provided on current legal compliance and any suggested amendments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>The Birch Package </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our âEssential HRâ package provides you with the HR foundations for your business, including Terms and Conditions and Employee Handbook. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\"><a href=\"http://whitetree.localhost/contact\">Contact us</a> for your Free Consultation today!  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customTextColor\":\"#606466\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#606466\" class=\"has-text-color\">Our packages serve as a guide. We are a bespoke HR Consultancy and will work with you to provide the right HR support for you and your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Packages','','inherit','closed','closed','','20-autosave-v1','','','2019-03-25 14:28:23','2019-03-25 14:28:23','',20,'http://whitetree.localhost/2019/03/25/20-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
